QuestData.Title: Mo'mor the Breaker
QuestData.Description: You must seek out Mo'mor immediately! You will find him in the center of Telaar, by the fountain. Tell him exactly what the ogre told you.
QuestData.LogDescription: Huntress Bintook at Telaar in Nagrand wants you to speak to Mo'mor the Breaker.
QuestData.RewardText: <Mo'mor looks perplexed.>$B$BSo, a new tribe of ogres is forcing the Boulderfist further and further south. This is quite troubling. We must first deal with the situation closest to home...
